{"tid":1386198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥民望跌至30.1分創上任新低  屬「表現拙劣」","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T09:56:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"37f294915e86774097b08e0f1af6160e2f718002","tid":1386198,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所公布自7月成立以來，第二份民意調查結果，民調於本月17至19日進行，隨機抽樣電話訪問1002名18歲或以上的香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n民調結果與上一次比較，特首林鄭月娥民望評分，顯著下跌3.3分至30.1分，反對率達70%，支持率為21%，再創其上任新低。<br />\n<br />\n至於特區政府滿意及信任淨值方面，分別為負52個百分點及負31個百分點。滿意率及信任比率分別為18% 及29%，而不滿意率及不信任比率分別為70%及60%，民望數字與一個月前相若。<br />\n<br />\n民情指數亦較7月上旬下跌4.5至67.4。而市民對經濟、民生及政治狀況滿意程度當中，以政治最差，政治狀況的平均量值為1.5分，滿意率淨值比上次統計顯著下跌7個百分點。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471363-20190730.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471363-20190730.htm&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCudekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=be2eaa9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471363-20190730.htm&h=02e76f24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471363-20190730.htm</a>"},{"pid":"081ccea1ab7a53e87d7f3c3a6574384da81f366b","tid":1386198,"uid":4237,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:34:25.000Z","msg":"咁撚厚面皮，跌到落0分都冇用啦"},{"pid":"545b682c37d61e97c051ee0a9318b8a3beaf5ba3","tid":1386198,"uid":211461,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"林鄭：香港人 關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習大大俾我幾多分先重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5ffa1fb2248e7ce943960efe57684910f4b801","tid":1386198,"uid":738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"仲有30分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89a464